extends framework
append head
  title 贰叁叁课程管理
append style
  +stylesheet('/style/dashboard.css')
append script
  +javascript('/script/dashboard.js')
block container
  .row.margin-bottom
    .col-md-12.view-profile
      .col-md-4.view-cover
        .fill-parent.darken.text-center.position-container.vertical-center-ib
          .view-profile-summary.vertical-center
            img.view-photo-img.img-circle
            h3.view-nickname
            .view-status.hidden 没有任何课程记录
      .col-md-8.col-md-offset-4
        .view-profile-detail
          h2 公告版
            a.btn.btn-default.pull-right.edit-announcement.hidden(data-visibic='admin', href='#') 编辑
          .announcement
            .announcement-text
            textarea.form-control.announcement-editor.fill-parent.hidden
        .view-notification.hidden
          span.glyphicon.glyphicon-bell &nbsp;
          | 您有 25 条未读消息 -
          | “社区强迫症患者专项整治行动通告”、
          | “《治疗不能放弃》专题讲座”、
          | “2010级毕业设计论文提交已开放”
